Package terrapeer.vui.j3dui.navigate

Class Summary
AvatarCamera Creates an actuator group that serves as a camera simulation.
AvatarCameraControl Creates a controller (draggers, filters, and mappers) for a Camera, which presumably has a view and possibly a headlight attached.
OrbitCamera Creates an actuator group that serves as a camera that orbits about the LAP.
OrbitCameraControl Creates a controller (draggers and mappers) for an OrbitCamera, which presumably has a view and possibly a headlight attached.
